comments: Barnes (TOR) makes contact to Caruso's (CHI) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball during his drive to the basket.
Ball (CHI) moves alongside of VanVleet (TOR) during the drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs prior to him losing his footing.
Ball (CHI) makes contact to VanVleet's (TOR) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
DeRozan (TOR) gathers the ball on his right foot and does not move his pivot foot prior to his shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) slides his pivot foot upon gathering the ball.
DeRozan (CHI) legally contests Anunoby's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Achiuwa (TOR) briefly places two hands on Vucevic (CHI) and the contact is marginal as he releases.
Achiuwa (TOR) moves laterally into DeRozan (CHI) and the body contact affects his SQBR.
Anunoby (TOR) moves forward into DeRozan (CHI) and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
Dragic (TOR) places an arm around Caruso's (CHI) opposite-side hip and the contact affects his FOM during the throw-in.
The Bulls signal for a timeout and are awarded the timeout prior to any possible foul or violation.
Replay review of the out-of-bounds call pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  Dragic (TOR) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB and the Bulls retain possession.
Achiuwa (TOR) commits a take foul on Vucevic (CHI).
Vucevic (CHI) legally contests VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
